@startuml
title Stays4Pilgrims - Frontend and backend communication overview

skinparam componentStyle rectangle

component "Stays4Pilgrims Frontend" as FE
component "Stays4Pilgrims Backend" as BE

FE --> BE : Auth
FE --> BE : Accommodation browsing
FE --> BE : Comments
FE --> BE : Uploads
FE --> BE : Account updates
FE --> BE : Moderation actions

note bottom of FE
  Detailed flows:
  - communication-auth-flow.puml
  - communication-accommodation-flow.puml
  - communication-media-moderation-flow.puml
end note

note bottom of BE
  Main API groups:
  /auth
  /accounts
  /accommodations
  /comments
  /upload
end note

@enduml